Text: Contact InformationForwarded by Michael DanielsonHOUECT on AM Richard D Homich on AM To Michael Danielson Email cc Greg Griffin Email Subject Contact Information Michael I look forward to the creative brief and the opportunity to present our offering Would you please send us a few dates and times next week for us to review the current website I will ask Greg Griffin to assemble the resources on our side for this meeting Please keep the roundtable discussion with John Seely Brown in mind This forum helps executives from prominent companies eg JC Pennys NiemanMarcus Vail Resorts etc shape Internet business agendas I thought it might provide a convenient means for you to build alignment with key members of Loise Kitchens staff Greg will make sure you get the agenda details The scheduling details are Friday May am to am Omni Mandalay at Las Colinas East Las Colinas Boulevard Irving Texas Best regards Rich Homich Viant We build digital businesses office mobile Viant Townsend Street Suite San Francisco CA
